Housekeeping Manager – UAE experience is required
–
Abu Dhabi, Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates
Job Description
Housekeeping Manager – Abu Dhabi
Responsibilities
Supervision of the Housekeeping services working to the operating standards as defined by the client
Supervision of the housekeeping and soft services employees
Cleaning supervision of public areas
Training of employees
Essential Skills & Experience
Must currently be working as a Housekeeping Supervisor in a corporate services environment for a minimum of 3-5 years
Experience of working in the UAE / Gulf / Middle East is essential
Housekeeping and cleaning services experience within a corporate services organisation
Knowledge of floor scrubbing, polishing and shampooing machines and vacuum cleaners
Knowledge of cleaning wooden furniture, marble floors and walls and glasses and mirrors
Education
Diploma in Hotel Management
Candidate Profile
Aged between 30 – 35 years
Physically fit
